        " اَلسَّمَاءِ وَ اَلْكُسُوفِ فَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ «صَلاَتُهُمَا سَوَاءٌ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1509 - Abdul-Rahman ibn Abi Abdullah asked Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about windstorms, darkness in the sky, and eclipses.\nImam (as) replied: \"The prayer for all of them is the same”."
